reviewText: This dvd provides some step by step instructions for the quick weave.  However, there are gaps in those instructions.  And it is the missing pieces that I needed.
This dvd is ok if your just looking for ideas on new styles. But, the step by step instruction is done really well.

I by dvd to teach myself, daughters & young girls in our center how to do makeup & hair and we have learned so much. i have been compliments on both ends. step by step makeup, weaving & braiding step by step & Eyerotic. i learned how to look like a diva when i want to, and my girls know how to apply makeup & do hair the right way. i couldn't teach them i was a tomboy & my mothet looked like a ghost when she applied makeup, so you know i was no asking her. I'm Marvel
